A ansible playbook that installs kubernetes packages includes kubelet, kubeadm and kubectl with containerd as container runtime, then creates a cluster on master-1 and join all other master and worker nodes to the cluster automatically.

use below command run:
ansible-playbook <path>/Install_K8s.yaml -i <path>/hosts

the restul:
